            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-2">Emotional Avoidance</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600">Sometimes bingeing isn't about the food — it's about avoiding something else. Difficult conversations, uncomfortable emotions, or overwhelming responsibilities.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-neutral-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow md:col-span-2">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
